BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Gue8ar1Cvubv0J1Arkh4f
SUMMARY:2026 Art BFA Exhibition
DTSTAMP:20260325T050853Z
DTSTART:20260404T010000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Cornish College of the Arts at Seattle University's Art Dep
	artment is proud to present the 2026 Art BFA Exhibition\, hosted at the 9t
	h Ave Gallery in South Lake Union. This exhibition features the work of 12
	 graduating students\, and is a cumulation of the skills and training they
	 have recieved throughout their time at Cornish. \n\nFeatured Artists:\n\n
	Webb Akamine-Rogers\n\nMatthes Boyd\n\nKyla Crockett\n\nChristy Gibson\n\n
	Jed Judt\n\nKaila Macaluso\n\nMadeline McKinney\n\nSean Minchak\n\nCloe Sh
	ort\n\nSelena Tacazon\n\nMason Webb\n\nSeher Taj\n\n \n\nOpening Reception
	:\n\nApril 3rd - 6pm - 9pm\n\n \n\nOn View:\n\nApril 3rd - April 17th\, 20
	26\n\nMon - Fri. - 10am - 4pm Sat. & Sun - 12pm - 4pm \n\nLocation: 9th Av
	e. Gallery - 2014 9th Ave\, Seattle\, WA 98121\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity
