DESCRIPTION:RAISED By TV brings you:30 Rock Trivia Night!50 BRAND NEW quest
	ions about your favs TGS gang.Covering the first 3 seasons Tues April 21st
	 7pm$7 ONLINE ADVANCE: {plus ticketing fees}$9 Day of & AT THE DOOR {plus 
	ticketing fees}Doors open at 6:00. Trivia starts at 7:00!Tables are first 
	come first serve.Venue is 21+ after 8pm THE CLOCK-OUT LOUNGE4864 Beacon Av
	e SSeattle\\\, WA 98108 **PRIZES**The RAISED BY TV gang has put together s
	ome killer prize packages. Teams of 1-5 are welcome. Prizes for 1st\\\, 2n
	d\\\, t have to be good at trivia just come on down to relive some TGS ant
	ics with us. **FOOD & DRINKS**The Clock-Out has bar and full Stevies Famou
	s Pizza food service\; one of the things that makes it our favorite place.
	The show is available on Amazon Prime\\\, Hulu and PeacockWe hope you can 
	join RbyTV for a safe night of fun and brains.Brandon Ryan\n\nhttps://cloc
	koutlounge.com/event/raised-by-tv-events-presents-30-rock-trivia-night/\n\
